---
---
<section class="why" id="porque">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Más que chocolate</span>
      <h2>Un detalle que emociona antes de abrirse</h2>
      <p>Desde 1903, elaboramos chocolate premium con el auténtico sabor y tradición boliviana.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="benefits-grid">
      <article class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-icon">✦</div>
        <h3>Experiencia de Regalo</h3>
        <p>Presentaciones de lujo diseñadas para convertir cada obsequio en un momento memorable.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-icon">◆</div>
        <h3>Chocolate premium</h3>
        <p>Una percepción superior desde el primer vistazo: brillo, textura, empaque y detalle.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-icon">◐</div>
        <h3>Presentación elegante</h3>
        <p>Diseño visual limpio, sofisticado y memorable para diferenciarse de un regalo común.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-icon">♥</div>
        <h3>Momentos inolvidables</h3>
        <p>No es solo chocolate: es la tradición e historia que compartes en cada momento especial.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    padding: 92px 20px;
  }

  .why {
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 12% 10%, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.16), transparent 24%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #FFF8FA 0%, #F6D5E5 100%);
  }

  .container {
    width: min(1120px, 100%);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-head {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto 48px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    color: var(--rose-wine);
    justify-content: center;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .eyebrow::before {
    content: "";
    width: 34px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--rose-wine);
  }

  .section-head h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 0.96;
    font-size: clamp(2.35rem, 5vw, 4.7rem);
    color: var(--berry-dark);
    letter-spacing: -0.045em;
  }

  .section-head p {
    margin: 18px auto 0;
    font-size: 1.06rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(42, 22, 18, 0.74);
  }

  .benefits-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 18px;
  }

  .benefit-card {
    border: 1px solid rgba(122, 30, 77, 0.12);
    background: rgba(255, 248, 250, 0.72);
    border-radius: 30px;
    padding: 28px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 55px rgba(122, 30, 77, 0.10);
    backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
  }

  .benefit-icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), #F7E3A6);
    box-shadow: 0 14px 32px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.24);
    color: #3A1A08;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .benefit-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--berry-dark);
    font-size: 1.42rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  }

  .benefit-card p {
    color: rgba(42, 22, 18, 0.72);
    line-height: 1.68;
    margin: 12px 0 0;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .benefits-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    section {
      padding: 68px 16px;
    }
    .benefits-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .benefit-card {
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: 26px;
    }
  }
</style>
